description: Xander is all about having a healthy mind and body, and you can tell he takes it seriously! He has a positive outlook on life, meditates, and he’s in school for personal training. Don’t let his small physique fool you, he’s an energetic guy that seems to get what he wants. Even though he hasn’t had anybody play with his cute little ass before, he’s open to it, “I’ve never done it, but I’m definitely willing to try it! I think it would be kinda cool. I think it would be kinda hot.”
title: Xander
